@node author "How to contact me"

				AUTHOR

I  am  26  years old,  study Physics at Bielefeld  University and like
stargazing a lot.  "Timer" was  written using SAS C 5.10b on an  Amiga
500 with 2.3 MB of RAM, KS 2.04 and an 80 MB Quantum HD with Evolution
Controller hardware/software.  I hate  cars, love bicycles, and I like
to get postcards from places where no (wo)man has gone before, so drop
me a line or two if you feel like it.

